Program: Outlook
Title: Together After 19 Years
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p04qsrrd
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 3 Feb 2017
Melake and Senbetu - the Eritrean couple who were reunited after nearly 20 years apart. Sissel Tolaas - the smell collector from Norway. She travels the world gathering smells and has even made a cheese from the smell of David Beckham's football boots. Ana Obarrio - Argentina's 83-year-old tennis champion on how she overcame personal challenges to revive her sporting career. Image: Couple at a sunset Credit: Getty Images Show less